---
import Layout from '@/components/AppLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '@/data/site.config';

const today = new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 10);
---

<Layout
  siteConfig={siteConfig}
  title="Terms · Listing Audit Tools"
  description="Terms of use for the listing-audit tool — free use, no warranty, not professional advice."
  path="/terms/"
>
  <section class="bg-parchment">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 pt-12 pb-16">
      <p class="label text-[color:var(--accent-700)]">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-serif text-h1 text-navy leading-tight">
        Terms of use<span class="period-accent">.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-caption text-ink-3 font-mono">
        Last updated <time datetime={today}>{today}</time>
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Use of the audit tool</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        The Listing Audit Tool is provided free of charge to short-term-rental
        hosts who own or operate a property listed on Airbnb, VRBO, or
        equivalent platform. You may use the generated audit report for your
        own listings or for client listings without attribution. You may not
        resell the audit-generation service itself or scrape audit reports for
        a competing tool.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-serif text-h2 text-navy">No warranty</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        The audit is generated by automated analysis and large-language-model
        evaluation. It is provided "as is," without warranty of any kind.
        Recommendations are general best-practice signals — they are not
        guaranteed to improve your listing's bookings, ranking, or revenue,
        and they do not constitute professional marketing, legal, or
        tax advice.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        Some audit checks compare your listing against patterns observed
        across thousands of other listings. The comparison is statistical, not
        causal. A listing with a "perfect" score can still underperform; a
        listing with a "poor" score can still rank highly.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Rate limits and abuse</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        Free use is rate-limited per IP address (see Privacy for details on
        how we identify visitors). Automated scraping, bulk-audit requests
        intended to circumvent rate limits, and any attempt to obtain audit
        output for a competing tool are prohibited and will result in IP-level
        suspension.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Email-gated reports</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        If you request the full PDF version of your audit, we will ask for
        your email address to deliver it. By submitting that email, you agree
        to receive the PDF and an occasional related newsletter (max 1 per
        week). You can unsubscribe with one click at any time.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Liability</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, we disclaim all liability for
        any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising
        from your use of the audit tool or reliance on the audit output. Our
        total liability, if any, is limited to the amount you have paid us
        for the audit (which, for free audits, is $0).
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Changes</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        We may update these terms as the product changes. The "Last updated"
        date at the top of this page tracks the current version. Continued
        use of the tool after a change constitutes acceptance.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Contact</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        Questions about these terms: <a class="underline" href="mailto:hello@strlistingaudit.tools">hello@strlistingaudit.tools</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
